{"tid":1626501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"法覆核緊急法、臨時禁制反蒙面法","createTime":"2019-10-05T11:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:38:07.000Z","uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8956caaaf3b18894cccf47bcf5f805b73437454f","tid":1626501,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"民主派全體24位議員已經正式入禀高等法院，要求法庭就《反蒙面法》頒下臨時禁制令，以及司法覆核緊急法。我們認為緊急法和基本法相抵觸，篡奪《基本法》賦予立法會的立法權，因此透過緊急法定立的《反蒙面法》亦不應有法律效力。<br />\n<br />\n嘩有排玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0db3c3a5372f0f7c096dd1a47b3daa342a80ca9","tid":1626501,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:34:40.000Z","msg":"24個泛民全部入<br />\n唔知幾時開始審"},{"pid":"5b3aa2834cc36353f43d4208e9443093d2e78524","tid":1626501,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:38:07.000Z","msg":"就算10月底高院話林鄭違反基本法。 <br />\n政府就會打上終審。同時仲繼續行蒙面法。 <br />\n最後係終審 審前......<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人大釋法</span></span>"}]}